interval="0" tabs_alignment="dfd-left-tabs"][vc_tab title="Visual Composer Builder" tab_id="e44ce9c0-2f4e-9"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_single_image image="13755" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]Convenient and fast best selling WordPress builder plugin. We've included it to the theme so you can get it for free and enjoy easy modifying your web site. Use both classic and backend editors, copy modules and whole rows, and create the site effortless.
Also, Visual Composer can be easily combined with most popular plugins, so you can get even more advanced web tool. Speed enhancement, SEO, analytics - everything will run smoothly and bring more benefits.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="8 Headers variants" tab_id="9790a86b-c9ac-9"][vc_single_image image="13757" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]Place your site navigation with these 8 completely modifying headers. No matter what you need - classic top header, minimalistic menu button, side navigation - you'll find one that will suit your needs. Moreover, header can be positioned at the top or bottom of the screen, with logo at the left, right or centered, you may select different background color, images and set transparency.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][ult_buttons btn_title="VIEW ALL HEADERS FULL DESCRIPTION PAGES" btn_align="ubtn-center" btn_size="ubtn-custom" btn_title_color="#2b2b2b" btn_bg_color="#ffffff" btn_hover="ubtn-no-hover-bg" btn_anim_effect="none" icon_size="32" btn_icon_pos="ubtn-sep-icon-at-left" btn_border_size="1" btn_radius="0" btn_shadow_size="5" enable_tooltip="" tooltip_pos="left" btn_link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fthemes.dfd.name%2Fronneby%2Fheaders%2F|title:8%20HEADERS|target:%20_blank" btn_bg_color_hover="#8a8f6a" btn_title_color_hover="#ffffff" btn_padding_left="390" btn_padding_top="15" btn_border_style="solid" btn_color_border="#eaeaea" btn_color_border_hover="#8a8f6a"][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Extended custom typography" tab_id="1427375801254-2-4"][vc_single_image image="13759" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]You can style all the theme fonts from this options' section. Here you may see separate fields for titles and subtitles H1-H6 styles, for blog and widget titles, block and feature titles, box names, info box subtitles, meta typography and main text settings.
You may select the font family, style and weight, size, letter and word spacing, line height and color. The theme will automatically add new fonts after they are selected in the options panel for typography, so you don't have to worry about assigning them properly.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Amazing scrolling content module" tab_id="1427375802195-3-7"][vc_single_image image="13761" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]We've created awesome module with the scrolling effect.You may set any background video or image for it and watch the content blocks slide over it while you scroll the page.It gives you the possibility to add one page scroll effect to usual layout type.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][ult_buttons btn_title="VIEW LAYOUT WITH SCROLLING CONTENT MODULE" btn_align="ubtn-center" btn_size="ubtn-block" btn_title_color="#353535" btn_bg_color="#f4f4f4" btn_hover="ubtn-no-hover-bg" btn_anim_effect="none" icon_size="32" btn_icon_pos="ubtn-sep-icon-at-left" btn_border_size="1" btn_radius="3" btn_shadow_size="5" enable_tooltip="" tooltip_pos="left" btn_link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fthemes.dfd.name%2Fronneby%2Fthird%2F|title:Scrolling%20content%20layout|target:%20_blank" btn_bg_color_hover="#4f4f4f" btn_title_color_hover="#ffffff"][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Megamenu options available" tab_id="1427375802791-4-5"][vc_single_image image="13763" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]Create Enable mega menu option to change the way your menu aligns. This opion allows you to display all the submenus grouped under their so called subcategories. Also, with the mega menu enabled, you can add different background images, icons, subtitles to the menu as well as select whether to display it full width or not.
Style the menu to display all the needed navigation easily understandable and conveniently.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Customizable footer" tab_id="1427375803431-5-3"][vc_single_image image="13764" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]Select one of the 3 variants or disable footer at all. Choose whether you need to display the subfooter. You may also style whether to display logo, social icons, menu, copyright message, etc.There are also options to set the background color or image both for footer and subfooter.
And, as a bonus, you can enable the parallax option for footer to make the layout content slide over it and uncover the footer while scrolling to the bottom.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][ult_buttons btn_title="CHECK PARALLAX FOOTER EFFECT" btn_link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fthemes.dfd.name%2Fronneby%2Ffirst%2F|title:Parallax%20footer|target:%20_blank" btn_align="ubtn-center" btn_size="ubtn-block" btn_title_color="#353535" btn_bg_color="#f4f4f4" btn_hover="ubtn-no-hover-bg" btn_anim_effect="none" btn_bg_color_hover="#4f4f4f" btn_title_color_hover="#ffffff" icon_size="32" btn_icon_pos="ubtn-sep-icon-at-left" btn_border_size="1" btn_radius="3" btn_shadow_size="5" enable_tooltip="" tooltip_pos="left"][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="23 portfolio hover variants" tab_id="1427375803996-6-3"][vc_single_image image="13766" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]Stylish portfolio needs sharp hovers as well.We've elaborated 23hover variants for portfolio, to be sure they'll fit any kind of the site. You may set one hover type for the whole page, or use different on separate portfolio elements.
Use bordered, with overlays, black-and-white, with titles or full thumb clickable, you'll definitely find suitable variant.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][ult_buttons btn_title="VIEW ALL HOVER VARIANTS" btn_align="ubtn-center" btn_size="ubtn-block" btn_title_color="#353535" btn_bg_color="#f4f4f4" btn_hover="ubtn-no-hover-bg" btn_anim_effect="none" icon_size="32" btn_icon_pos="ubtn-sep-icon-at-left" btn_border_size="1" btn_radius="3" btn_shadow_size="5" enable_tooltip="" tooltip_pos="left" btn_link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fthemes.dfd.name%2Fronneby%2Fportfolio-hovers%2F|title:HOVER%20VARIANTS|target:%20_blank" btn_bg_color_hover="#4f4f4f" btn_title_color_hover="#ffffff"][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="48 styled widgets" tab_id="1427375804567-7-5"][vc_single_image image="13767" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]You'll probably use sidebars.And sidebars will contain widgets. All of our widgets are perfectly shaped to fit the theme's color scheme and style. You may type titles and use pre-built styling classes for the sidebars.
You may add login form, recent works, products, posts, facebook or flickr feeds, tags and much more.Up to 48 nice and useful widgets are waiting for you to use.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Columns, modules and rows parallax" tab_id="1427375805129-8-0"][vc_single_image image="13769" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]Row parallax is definitely a great function. And columns and modules parallax is even better option. You can use various backgrounds for parallax effects to underline some part of your site and trigger attention.
You can create amazing effects on two modules parallaxing with different speed, using shop product parallax or parallaxing both row background and module in it, etc. All of these will turn visiting your site into amazing experience.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][ult_buttons btn_title="VIEW COLUMN PARALLAX LAYOUT" btn_align="ubtn-center" btn_size="ubtn-block" btn_title_color="#353535" btn_bg_color="#f4f4f4" btn_hover="ubtn-no-hover-bg" btn_anim_effect="none" icon_size="32" btn_icon_pos="ubtn-sep-icon-at-left" btn_border_size="1" btn_radius="3" btn_shadow_size="5" enable_tooltip="" tooltip_pos="left" btn_link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fthemes.dfd.name%2Fronneby%2Ffirst%2F|title:Column%20parallax|target:%20_blank" btn_bg_color_hover="#4f4f4f" btn_title_color_hover="#ffffff"][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Incredible shop layouts" tab_id="1427375805721-9-0"][vc_single_image image="13770" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]Check our stylish shops and use them for your ecommerce web site. You may choose some extravagant variant with full thumbs and hover description on the shop homepage. Or you may keep it simple and stay with the traditional all products presentation. Also, you may use both of them to achieve the best combination and user experience on your web site.
No matter what option will you choose - to amaze with the structure or to make it simple and sharp, you'll definitely have enough tools for implementation with Ronneby theme.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][ult_buttons btn_title="VIEW ALL SHOP LAYOUTS" btn_align="ubtn-center" btn_size="ubtn-block" btn_title_color="#353535" btn_bg_color="#f4f4f4" btn_hover="ubtn-no-hover-bg" btn_anim_effect="none" icon_size="32" btn_icon_pos="ubtn-sep-icon-at-left" btn_border_size="1" btn_radius="3" btn_shadow_size="5" enable_tooltip="" tooltip_pos="left" btn_link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fthemes.dfd.name%2Fronneby%2F%23|title:promo|target:%20_blank" btn_bg_color_hover="#4f4f4f" btn_title_color_hover="#ffffff"][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="18 demo layouts" tab_id="1427376053643-10-6"][vc_single_image image="14032" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]You cansee all the variants of the modules application before using the theme.You may find the already created layout that you'll be able to modify to get the desired look or copy the modules' structure from it.
Anyway this is not the complete list and you're not limited in realization your ideas. You may also suggest us a new layout and we'll create it with all the powerful options the theme has.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][ult_buttons btn_title="VIEW ALL PROMO LAYUTS" btn_align="ubtn-center" btn_size="ubtn-block" btn_title_color="#353535" btn_bg_color="#f4f4f4" btn_hover="ubtn-no-hover-bg" btn_anim_effect="none" icon_size="32" btn_icon_pos="ubtn-sep-icon-at-left" btn_border_size="1" btn_radius="3" btn_shadow_size="5" enable_tooltip="" tooltip_pos="left" btn_link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fthemes.dfd.name%2Fronneby%2F%23|title:Promo|target:%20_blank" btn_bg_color_hover="#4f4f4f" btn_title_color_hover="#ffffff"][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="One click demo import" tab_id="1427376054584-11-8"][vc_single_image image="13772" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]All the import process is optimized and elaborated to make it easy, fast and convenient.You may upload Blog posts and Portfolio items with the Main content.Any of the other demo layouts you may upload inone click in the Installer Panel section of your Dashboard.
You may use entire layout as it is (just replace the images and texts with your own) or combine different elements from all layouts.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Lots of supported plugins" tab_id="1427376056079-12-0"][vc_single_image image="13773" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]As far as Visual Composer is one of the most popular tools to create sites, it's compatible with lots of plugins you may need to use.So you may be sure that you'll find suitable solution to implement ll your creative ideas.
However, you may contact us to check the plugin for theme compatibility before using it on your live site.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Premium plugins included" tab_id="1427376056880-13-6"][vc_single_image image="13777" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]You may enjoy the usage of the Premium plugins on your site - Visual Composer, Ultimate Addons for Visual Composer and Revolution Slider.We'll provide you with all the plugins updates for convenient work on your projects.
As you see, you save 68$ on plugins with our theme. Such a profitable purchase.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Prebuilt styles for Contact Form 7" tab_id="1427376057672-14-6"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_single_image image="13779" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]Get the feedback from your visitors with this wonderful Contact Form 7 plugin.We've worked on it to make it suit the style of the site perfectly. You may add any contact fields you need to receive all the needed information.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][ult_buttons btn_title="CONTACT FORM STYLES PAGE" btn_align="ubtn-center" btn_size="ubtn-block" btn_title_color="#353535" btn_bg_color="#f4f4f4" btn_hover="ubtn-no-hover-bg" btn_anim_effect="none" icon_size="32" btn_icon_pos="ubtn-sep-icon-at-left" btn_border_size="1" btn_radius="3" btn_shadow_size="5" enable_tooltip="" tooltip_pos="left" btn_link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fthemes.dfd.name%2Fronneby%2Fshortcodes%2Fcontact-form-7%2F|title:Contact%20form%207|target:%20_blank" btn_bg_color_hover="#4f4f4f" btn_title_color_hover="#ffffff"][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="One page scroll option available" tab_id="1427376059293-16-3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_single_image image="13774" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]Display all the needed information slide by slide with this wonderful page template.You may use it as a skeleton for corporate website, portfolio presentation, even for the shop. And it'll look great performing all those functions.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][ult_buttons btn_title="VIEW ALL ONEPAGE LAYOUTS" btn_align="ubtn-center" btn_size="ubtn-block" btn_title_color="#353535" btn_bg_color="#f4f4f4" btn_hover="ubtn-no-hover-bg" btn_anim_effect="none" icon_size="32" btn_icon_pos="ubtn-sep-icon-at-left" btn_border_size="1" btn_radius="3" btn_shadow_size="5" enable_tooltip="" tooltip_pos="left" btn_link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fthemes.dfd.name%2Fronneby%2F%23|title:Onepage%20layouts|target:%20_blank" btn_bg_color_hover="#4f4f4f" btn_title_color_hover="#ffffff"][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Multilingual ready" tab_id="1427376273897-17-2"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_single_image image="14033" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]We provide the theme translated into two languages (German and Russian) and with the files ready for translation and using with multilingual plugins.You may translate the theme into your language or use our ready translations.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Premium quality support" tab_id="1427376274586-18-5"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_single_image image="13775" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][ultimate_spacer height="25" height_on_tabs="20" height_on_mob="20"][vc_column_text]High quality and timely support is also included to the theme, so you may enjoy all the benefits of free solutions from real professionals.We'll do our best to help you with theme customization and getting more of it.
